      "text_block": {
        "title": "楼桑树下的种子",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f1_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "楼桑村的人都记得，刘家门前那棵大桑树高得像一把撑开的车盖。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f1_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "少年刘备常站在树下抬头看它，像在看一件本不该属于穷人的东西。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.0,
        "y": 0.0,
        "w": 1.0,
        "h": 0.2635
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f2",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p02_s1",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p02-page-01-f2",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "贵种压在穷日子里",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f2_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "可长大以后，他还是靠编草鞋、织草席过日子，先顾得上母亲的一碗热汤。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.0,
        "y": 0.2635,
        "w": 0.5054,
        "h": 0.2398
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f3",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p02_s2",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p02-page-01-f3",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "榜前长叹",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f3_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "招兵榜贴出来时，刘备一个字一个字看完，最后只剩下一声长叹。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f3_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "他叹的不是怕死，是胸中有志，手上却没有钱、没有人、没有兵。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.5054,
        "y": 0.2635,
        "w": 0.4946,
        "h": 0.2398
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f4",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p02_s3",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p02-page-01-f4",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "张飞一脚踏进来",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f4_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "身后忽然炸开一声厉喝。这个黑脸大汉不像路人，像一脚踏进来的雷。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.0,
        "y": 0.5033,
        "w": 0.5043,
        "h": 0.2303
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f5",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p02_s3",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p02-page-01-f5",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "一人有志，一人有财",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f5_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "刘备没有绕弯，只说自己想去破贼，可惜力不能及。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f5_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "张飞一听就亮了眼：志气你有，钱我来出，咱们现在就能动手。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.5043,
        "y": 0.5033,
        "w": 0.4957,
        "h": 0.2303
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f6",
      "scene_id": "cp001_p02_s3",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp001-p02-page-01-f6",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "第三个人快到了",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f6_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "两个人一拍即合，转身就进了村店。刘备忽然觉得，今天这口气叹得值。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f6_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "酒还没上来，门口先落下一道新的影子。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
